<h1> HTML Styles is all about styles. </h1>
<p> In this you will learn how to make text chage color, size and more! </p>
<p>I am normal</p>
<p style="color:purple;">I am Purple</p>
<p style="color:turquoise;">I am Turquoise</p>
<p style="font-size:36px;">I am BIG</p>
<p style="font-size:11px;">I am small</p>
<p> all of you try to type all 4 of these :</p>
<h3> for the color one's you type </h3>
<p style="color:red;"> -p style="color:your color here;">your text here -/p- 
<h3> for size you type: </h3> 
<p style="color:blue;"> -p style="font-size:#px;"> your text here -/p- </p>
<h1> like this here are some style's below! </h1>
<p style="color:red;"> I am Red
